text:
Example renv.lock file
In the following example:

The ‚ÄúR‚Äù section specifies the R version used in the project.
The ‚ÄúPackages‚Äù section lists the packages used, each with its name, version, and source (e.g., CRAN).
The ‚ÄúDependencies‚Äù section outlines the dependencies for each package, including both Imports and LinkingTo.

{
  "R": {
    "Version": "4.2.0"
  },
  "Packages": {
    "data.table": {
      "Package": "data.table",
      "Version": "1.14.0",
      "Source": "CRAN"
    },
    "ggplot2": {
      "Package": "ggplot2",
      "Version": "3.3.5",
      "Source": "CRAN"
    }
  },
  "Dependencies": {
    "data.table": {
      "Imports": [],
      "LinkingTo": []
    },
    "ggplot2": {
      "Imports": [
        "methods",
        "grDevices",
        "graphics",
        "stats"
      ],
      "LinkingTo": []
    }
  }
}
